            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Para começar a agrupar código relacionado, começamos codificando a palavra-chave <code>func</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"func\" class=\"keyword\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"0\" endIndex=\"4\" /></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>func</code>.</p></body></html>"
